          Number(Domestic AU Transfer): <strong>14058058</strong><br>Account
          Number(International Transfer): <strong>200014058058</strong><br>BSB
          Number:
          <strong>062-000</strong><br>ABA/SWIFT Code:
          <strong>CTBAAU2S</strong><br><br>Bank Name:<br><strong>Commonwealth Bank
          of Australia</strong><br><br>Bank Address:<br><strong>Darling Park,
          Tower 1,<br>201 Sussex Street Sydney<br>NSW 2000
          Australia</strong><br>
        </div>
      </td>
      <td style="vertical-align:top" valign="top">
        <div
             style="font-size:12px;line-height:20px;background-color:#f2f2f2;margin:4px;padding:12px">
          <div style="color:#383d49;font-weight:600">USD Denominated Deposits
          </div>Beneficiary Name: <strong>Bacera Co Pty Ltd</strong><br>Account
          Number: <strong>200015750601</strong><br>BSB Number:
          <strong>062-000</strong><br>ABA/SWIFT Code:
          <strong>CTBAAU2S</strong><br><br>Bank Name:<br><strong>Commonwealth Bank
          of Australia</strong><br><br>Bank Address:<br><strong>Darling Park,
          Tower 1,<br>
          201 Sussex Street Sydney<br>NSW 2000 Australia</strong><br>
