  </p>
  <p style="color: #cc1f1a; font-weight: 600">{{Reason}}</p>
  <br />
  <p>
    Хэрэв та хүсэлтээр ямарч шалтгаангүй байгаа бол, та таны дан менежертэй ярилцана уу, эсвэл бидэнтэй онлайн чатын дамжлаа авна уу.
  </p>
</div>
', '');
INSERT INTO cms."_TopicContent" ("Id", "TopicId", "CreatedOn", "UpdatedOn", "Language", "Title", "Author", "Content", "Subtitle") VALUES (11415, 11274, '2023-09-13 20:51:32.320751 +00:00', '2023-09-13 20:56:46.706149 +00:00', 'id-id', 'Penarikan Pelanggan Gagal', '', e'<div style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px">
  <p
     style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 24px"
     >
    Bapak/Ibu Mitra BCR yang terhormat,
  </p>
  <p>
    Permintaan penarikan nasabah Anda tidak dapat diproses dan telah ditolak. Rincian lebih lanjut disediakan di bawah ini:
  </p>
  <table
         class="letter-table"
         style="
                table-layout: fixed;
                line-height: 24px;
                margin-left: auto;
                margin-right: auto;
                text-align: left;
                padding: 8px;
                float: none;
                "
         bgcolor="#f2f2f2"
         align="left"
         >
    <tr>
      <th
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 color: #383d49;
                 white-space: nowrap;
                 "
          >
        Nomor Rekening:
      </th>
      <td
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 word-wrap: break-word;
                 "
          >
        {{AccountNumber}}
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 color: #383d49;
                 white-space: nowrap;
                 "
          >
        Nama Rekening:
      </th>
      <td
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 word-wrap: break-word;
                 "
          >
        {{NativeName}}
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 color: #383d49;
                 white-space: nowrap;
                 "
          >
        Mata Uang Rekening:
      </th>
      <td
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 word-wrap: break-word;
                 "
          >
        {{Currency}}
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 color: #383d49;
                 white-space: nowrap;
                 "
          >
        Jumlah Penarikan:
      </th>
      <td
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 word-wrap: break-word;
                 "
          >
        $ {{FormattedAmount}}
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 color: #383d49;
                 white-space: nowrap;
                 "
          >
        Tanggal Permintaan:
      </th>
      <td
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 word-wrap: break-word;
                 "
          >
        {{Date}}
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
  <p>
    Alasan mengapa permintaan penarikan tidak dapat diproses adalah sebagai berikut:
  </p>
  <p style="color: #cc1f1a; font-weight: 600">{{Reason}}</p>
  <br />
  <p>
    Jika Anda masih tidak yakin mengapa permintaan penarikan Anda ditolak, silakan berkonsultasi dengan manajer akun Anda atau hubungi kami melalui obrolan langsung.
  </p>
</div>
', ' ');
INSERT INTO cms."_TopicContent" ("Id", "TopicId", "CreatedOn", "UpdatedOn", "Language", "Title", "Author", "Content", "Subtitle") VALUES (11474, 11286, '2024-01-04 19:51:41.299305 +00:00', '2024-04-11 20:32:10.731477 +00:00', 'jp-jp', 'Client Daily Confirmation', '', e'
  <meta http-equiv="content-type" content="text/html;charset=utf-8" />
  <table
    align="center"
    style="
      width: 900px;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      font-family: \'微软雅黑\';
      padding: 5px 0px;
      -moz-border-radius: 5px;
      -webkit-border-radius: 5px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      border: 0px #ddcebd solid;
      background: url(https://s3.amazonaws.com/bcr-img-new/email/docs_bg.png)
        repeat-y;
      background-position: right 0 top 0;
    "
  >
    <tr>
      <td>
        <table style="width: 100%">
          <tr>
            <td
              style="
                text-align: left;
                line-height: 40px;
                        font-size: 32px;
                                                        font-family: \'Times New Roman\', Times, serif;
                                                    "
                                                >
                                                    <img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/bcr-img-new/bcr_logo.png" />
                                                </td>
                                            </tr>
                                        </table>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>
                                        <table style="width: 100%; font-size: 12px">
                                            <tr>
                                                <td style="width: 25%">
                                                    アカウント: <strong>@Model.AccountNumber</strong>
                                                </td>
                                                <td style="width: 25%">名前: <strong>@Model.NativeName</strong></td>
                                                <td style="width: 25%"></td>
                                                <td style="width: 25%; text-align: right">
                                                    @Model.ReportDate.ToString("yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss")
                    </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <table
                        style="
                            width: 100%;
                            font-size: 10px;
                            text-align: right;
                            line-height: 20px;
                            border-collapse: collapse;
                            border: 0px solid #cccccc;
                        "
                    >
                        <tr>
                            <td colspan="13" align="left">
                                <strong>クローズドトレード:</strong>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr
                            style="
                                background: #f5f5f5;
                                text-align: center;
                                border: 1px solid #cccccc;
                            "
                        >
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">チケット</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="12%">オープン時間</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">タイプ</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="6%">サイズ</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">アイテム</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">価格</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">S/L</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">T/P</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="12%">クローズ時間</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">価格</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">手数料</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">スワップ</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">トレードP/L</td>
                        </tr>
                        @{ var color = new[] { "#FFFFFF;", "#EEEEEE;" }; var counter = 0; }
                        @if (Model.ClosedTrades != null && Model.ClosedTrades.Count > 0) {
                        foreach (var trade in Model.ClosedTrades) {
                        <tr style="background: @color[counter++ % 2]">
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">@trade.Ticket</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">@trade.OpenAt.ToString("yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss")</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">@if(trade.Cmd == 1) { <text>Sell</text> } else if (trade.Cmd == 0){ <text>Buy</text>
    }
    else if (trade.Cmd == 6){ <text>Balance</text> }
</td>
    
                            @if (trade.Cmd < 2) {
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">@trade.Volume</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">@trade.Symbol</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:F" + trade.Digits + "}", trade.OpenPrice ?? 0)
                            </td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:F" + trade.Digits + "}", trade.Sl)
                            </td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:F" + trade.Digits + "}", trade.Tp)
                            </td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">@trade.CloseAt</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:F" + trade.Digits + "}", trade.ClosePrice ?? 0)
                            </td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:N2}", trade.Commission)
                            </td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:N2}", trade.Swaps)
                            </td>
                            } else if (trade.Cmd > 5) {
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" colspan="9" align="right">
                                @trade.Comment
                            </td>
                            }
    
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:N2}", trade.Profit)
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        } } else {
                        <tr style="background: #ffffff; text-align: center">
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" colspan="13">
                                トランザクションなし
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        }
    
                        <tr style="background: #eeeeee">
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" colspan="10"></td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:N2}", Model.ClosedTradeSummary.Commission)
                            </td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:N2}", Model.ClosedTradeSummary.Swaps)
                            </td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:N2}", Model.ClosedTradeSummary.Profit)
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <table style="width: 100%; font-size: 12px">
                        <tr>
                            <td>
                                <strong
                                    >入金/出金: @string.Format("{0:N2}",
                                    Model.ClosedTradeSummary.Deposit)</strong
                                >
                            </td>
                            <td>
                                <strong
                                    >信用取引: @string.Format("{0:N2}",
                                    Model.ClosedTradeSummary.Credit)</strong
                                >
                            </td>
                            <td style="text-align: right">
                                <strong
                                    >クローズトレードP/L:
                                    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@string.Format("{0:N2}",
                                    Model.ClosedTradeSummary.TotalProfit)</strong
                                >
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>&nbsp;</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <table
                        style="
                            width: 100%;
                            font-size: 10px;
                            text-align: right;
                            line-height: 20px;
                            border-collapse: collapse;
                            border: 0px solid #cccccc;
                        "
                    >
                        <tr>
                            <td colspan="12" align="left">
                                <strong>オープントレード:</strong>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr
                            style="
                                background: #f5f5f5;
                                text-align: center;
                                border: 1px solid #cccccc;
                                font-size: 11px;
                            "
                        >
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">チケット</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="12%">オープン時間</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">タイプ</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="6%">サイズ</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">アイテム</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">価格</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">S/L</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">T/P</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="12%">クローズ時間</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">価格</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">手数料</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">スワップ</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">トレードP/L</td>
                        </tr>
                        @{ counter = 0; } @if (Model.OpenTrades != null &&
                        Model.OpenTrades.Count > 0) { foreach (var trade in Model.OpenTrades)
                        { if (trade.Cmd < 2) {
                        <tr style="background: @color[counter++ % 2]">
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">@trade.Ticket</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">@trade.OpenAt.ToString("yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss")</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @if(trade.Cmd == 1) { <text>Sell</text> } else {
                                <text>Buy</text> }
                            </td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:f2}", trade.Volume)
                            </td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">@trade.Symbol</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:F" + trade.Digits + "}", trade.OpenPrice ?? 0)
                            </td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:F" + trade.Digits + "}", trade.Sl)
                            </td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:F" + trade.Digits + "}", trade.Tp)
                            </td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc"></td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:F" + trade.Digits + "}", trade.CurrentPrice ??
                                0)
                            </td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:N2}", trade.Commission)
                            </td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:N2}", trade.Swaps)
                            </td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:N2}", trade.Profit)
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        } } } else {
                        <tr style="background: #ffffff; text-align: center">
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" colspan="13">
                                トランザクションなし
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        }
    
                        <tr style="background: #eeeeee">
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" colspan="10"></td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:N2}", Model.OpenTradeSummary.Commission)
                            </td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:N2}", Model.OpenTradeSummary.Swaps)
                            </td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:N2}", Model.OpenTradeSummary.Profit)
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <table style="width: 100%; font-size: 12px; border-collapse: collapse">
                        <tr>
                            <td><strong>&nbsp;</strong></td>
                            <td align="right">
                                <strong
                                    >浮動P/L:&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; @string.Format("{0:N2}",
                                Model.OpenTradeSummary.TotalProfit)</strong
                                >
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>&nbsp;</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <table
                        style="
                            width: 100%;
                            font-size: 10px;
                            text-align: right;
                            line-height: 20px;
                            border-collapse: collapse;
                        "
                    >
                        <tr>
                            <td colspan="12" align="left"><strong>未処理注文:</strong></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr style="background: #eeeeee; text-align: center">
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">チケット</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="12%">オープン時間</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">タイプ</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="6%">サイズ</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">アイテム</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">価格</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">S/L</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="7%">S/P</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="12%">市場価格</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" width="28%"></td>
                        </tr>
                        @{ counter = 0; } @if (Model.PendingTrades != null &&
                        Model.PendingTrades.Count > 0) { foreach (var trade in
                        Model.PendingTrades) {
                        <tr style="background: @color[counter++ % 2]">
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">@trade.Ticket</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">@trade.OpenAt.ToString("yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss")</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">@if(trade.Cmd == 1) { <text>Sell</text> } else { <text>Buy</text> }</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:f2}", trade.Volume)
                            </td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">@trade.Symbol</td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:F" + trade.Digits + "}", trade.OpenPrice ?? 0)
                            </td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:F" + trade.Digits + "}", trade.Sl)
                            </td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:F" + trade.Digits + "}", trade.Tp)
                            </td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">
                                @string.Format("{0:F" + trade.Digits + "}", trade.ClosePrice ?? 0)
                            </td>
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc">@trade.Comment</td>
                        </tr>
                        } } else {
                        <tr style="background: #eeeeee; text-align: center">
                            <td style="border: 1px solid #cccccc" colspan="10">
                                未処理注文なし
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        }
                    </table>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <table
                        style="
                            width: 100%;
                            font-size: 12px;
                            text-align: right;
                            line-height: 20px;
                        "
                    >
                        <tr>
                            <td colspan="4" align="left"><strong>A/C サマリー:</strong></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td style="width: 25%; text-align: left">前日の残高:</td>
                            <td style="width: 25%">
                                <strong
                                    >@string.Format("{0:N2}", Model.Summary.PrevBalance)</strong
                                >
                            </td>
                            <td style="width: 25%">浮動P/L:</td>
                            <td style="width: 25%; text-align: right">
                                <strong
                                    >@string.Format("{0:N2}",
                                    Model.OpenTradeSummary.TotalProfit)</strong
                                >
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td style="width: 25%; text-align: left">クローズトレードP/L:</td>
                            <td style="width: 25%">
                                <strong
                                    >@string.Format("{0:N2}",
                                    Model.ClosedTradeSummary.Profit)</strong
                                >
                            </td>
                            <td style="width: 25%">信用:</td>
                            <td style="width: 25%; text-align: right">
                                <strong
                                    >@string.Format("{0:N2}", Model.Summary.Credit)</strong
                                >
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td style="width: 25%; text-align: left">入金/出金:</td>
                            <td style="width: 25%">
                                <strong
                                    >@string.Format("{0:N2}", Model.Summary.Deposit /
                                    100)</strong
                                >
                            </td>
                            <td style="width: 25%">資産:</td>
                            <td style="width: 25%; text-align: right">
                                <strong
                                    >@string.Format("{0:N2}", (Model.Summary.Balance +
                                    Model.Summary.Credit +
                                    Model.OpenTradeSummary.TotalProfit))</strong
                                >
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td style="width: 25%; text-align: left">残高:</td>
                            <td style="width: 25%">
                                <strong
                                    >@string.Format("{0:N2}", Model.Summary.Balance)</strong
                                >
                            </td>
                            <td style="width: 25%">証拠金必要額:</td>
                            <td style="width: 25%; text-align: right">
                                <strong
                                    >@string.Format("{0:N2}", Model.Summary.Margin)</strong
                                >
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                            <td style="width: 25%">&nbsp;</td>
                            <td style="width: 25%">&nbsp;</td>
                            <td style="width: 25%">利用可能な証拠金:</td>
                            <td style="width: 25%; text-align: right">
                                <strong
                                    >@string.Format("{0:N2}", (Model.Summary.Balance +
                                    Model.Summary.Credit + Model.OpenTradeSummary.TotalProfit -
                                    Model.Summary.Margin))</strong
                                >
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td>&nbsp;</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td align="left" style="font-size: 12px">よろしくお願い申し上げます</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td align="left" style="font-size: 12px">BCR</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td align="center" style="font-size: 10px">
                    この明細に誤りがある場合、48時間以内にお知らせください。それ以外の場合、この明細はあなたによって確認されたものとみなされます。
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td align="center" style="font-size: 10px">
                    浮動損益および資産の数値は、レポートの生成時点の価格に基づいて計算されており、実際の終値と異なる場合があります。
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
    ', '');
INSERT INTO cms."_TopicContent" ("Id", "TopicId", "CreatedOn", "UpdatedOn", "Language", "Title", "Author", "Content", "Subtitle") VALUES (11416, 11274, '2023-09-13 20:53:09.329820 +00:00', '2023-09-13 20:59:03.458488 +00:00', 'ms-my', 'Pengeluaran Pelanggan Gagal', '', e'<div style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px">
  <p
     style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 24px"
     >
    Tuan/Puan Rakan BCR yang dihormati,
  </p>
  <p>
    Permintaan penarikan pelanggan anda tidak dapat diproses dan telah ditolak. Maklumat lanjut diberikan di bawah:
  </p>
  <table
         class="letter-table"
         style="
                table-layout: fixed;
                line-height: 24px;
                margin-left: auto;
                margin-right: auto;
                text-align: left;
                padding: 8px;
                float: none;
                "
         bgcolor="#f2f2f2"
         align="left"
         >
    <tr>
      <th
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 color: #383d49;
                 white-space: nowrap;
                 "
          >
        Nombor Akaun:
      </th>
      <td
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 word-wrap: break-word;
                 "
          >
        {{AccountNumber}}
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 color: #383d49;
                 white-space: nowrap;
                 "
          >
        Nama Akaun:
      </th>
      <td
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 word-wrap: break-word;
                 "
          >
       {{NativeName}}
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 color: #383d49;
                 white-space: nowrap;
                 "
          >
        Mata Wang Akaun:
      </th>
      <td
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 word-wrap: break-word;
                 "
          >
       {{Currency}}
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 color: #383d49;
                 white-space: nowrap;
                 "
          >
        Jumlah Penarikan:
      </th>
      <td
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 word-wrap: break-word;
                 "
          >
        $ {{FormattedAmount}}
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 color: #383d49;
                 white-space: nowrap;
                 "
          >
        Tarikh Permintaan:
      </th>
      <td
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 word-wrap: break-word;
                 "
          >
      {{Date}}
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
  <p>
    Alasan mengapa permintaan penarikan tidak dapat diproses adalah seperti berikut:
  </p>
  <p style="color: #cc1f1a; font-weight: 600">{{Reason}}</p>
  <br />
  <p>
    Jika anda masih tidak pasti mengapa permintaan penarikan anda ditolak, sila berunding dengan pengurus akaun anda atau hubungi kami melalui perbualan langsung.
  </p>
</div>
', ' ');
INSERT INTO cms."_TopicContent" ("Id", "TopicId", "CreatedOn", "UpdatedOn", "Language", "Title", "Author", "Content", "Subtitle") VALUES (10050, 11250, '2023-08-16 01:12:08.273107 +00:00', '2024-06-21 22:51:28.183222 +00:00', 'zh-tw', '存款成功', '', e'<div style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px">
  <p style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 24px">
    親愛的 BCR 客戶，
  </p>
  <p>
    請查看以下的存款詳細資訊：
  </p>
  <table class="letter-table" style="
                      table-layout: fixed;
                      line-height: 24px;
                      margin-left: auto;
                      margin-right: auto;
                      text-align: left;
                      padding: 8px;
                      float: none;
                    " bgcolor="#f2f2f2" align="left">
    <tr>
      <th style="
                          padding-left: 24px;
                          padding-right: 24px;
                          color: #383d49;
                          white-space: nowrap;
                        ">
        帳號:
      </th>
      <td style="
                          padding-left: 24px;
                          padding-right: 24px;
                          word-wrap: break-word;
                        ">
        {{AccountNumber}}
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th style="
                          padding-left: 24px;
                          padding-right: 24px;
                          color: #383d49;
                          white-space: nowrap;
                        ">
        客戶組:
      </th>
    
    <td style="
                          padding-left: 24px;
                          padding-right: 24px;
                          word-wrap: break-word;
                        ">
      {{Group}}
    </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th style="
                          padding-left: 24px;
                          padding-right: 24px;
                          color: #383d49;
                          white-space: nowrap;
                        ">
        電子郵件:
      </th>
      <td style="
                          padding-left: 24px;
                          padding-right: 24px;
                          word-wrap: break-word;
                        ">
        {{UserEmail}}
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th style="
                          padding-left: 24px;
                          padding-right: 24px;
                          color: #383d49;
                          white-space: nowrap;
                        ">
        電話:
      </th>
      <td style="
                          padding-left: 24px;
                          padding-right: 24px;
                          word-wrap: break-word;
                        ">
        {{UserPhone}}
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th style="
                          padding-left: 24px;
                          padding-right: 24px;
                          color: #383d49;
                          white-space: nowrap;
                        ">
        帳戶名稱:
      </th>
      <td style="
                          padding-left: 24px;
                          padding-right: 24px;
                          word-wrap: break-word;
                        ">
        {{NativeName}}
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th style="
                          padding-left: 24px;
                          padding-right: 24px;
                          color: #383d49;
                          white-space: nowrap;
                        ">
        付款編號:
      </th>
      <td style="
                          padding-left: 24px;
                          padding-right: 24px;
                          word-wrap: break-word;
                        ">
        {{PaymentNumber}}
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th style="
                          padding-left: 24px;
                          padding-right: 24px;
                          color: #383d49;
                          white-space: nowrap;
                        ">
        存款金額:
      </th>
      <td style="
                          padding-left: 24px;
                          padding-right: 24px;
                          word-wrap: break-word;
                        ">
        $ {{FormattedAmount}}
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th style="
                          padding-left: 24px;
                          padding-right: 24px;
                          color: #383d49;
                          white-space: nowrap;
                        ">
        存款日期:
      </th>
      <td style="
                          padding-left: 24px;
                          padding-right: 24px;
                          word-wrap: break-word;
                        ">
        {{Date}}
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</div>
', '');
INSERT INTO cms."_TopicContent" ("Id", "TopicId", "CreatedOn", "UpdatedOn", "Language", "Title", "Author", "Content", "Subtitle") VALUES (10051, 11251, '2023-08-16 01:13:26.994856 +00:00', '2023-08-23 22:24:20.957620 +00:00', 'zh-tw', '提现確認', '', e'<div style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px">
  <p style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 24px">
    尊敬的客戶，
  </p>
  <p>
    您的提款請求已經處理完成。請允許1-2個工作日將資金存入您的銀行帳戶。您的參考編號為{{ReferenceNumber}}。
    以下提供更多詳細信息：
  </p>
  <table
         class="letter-table"
         style="
                table-layout: fixed;
                line-height: 24px;
                margin-left: auto;
                margin-right: auto;
                text-align: left;
                padding: 8px;
                float: none;
                "
         bgcolor="#f2f2f2"
         align="left"
         >
    <tr>
      <th
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 color: #383d49;
                 white-space: nowrap;
                 "
          >
        提款方式：
      </th>
      <td
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 word-wrap: break-word;
                 "
          >
        {{PaymentMethod}}
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 color: #383d49;
                 white-space: nowrap;
                 "
          >
        帳戶編號：
      </th>
      <td
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 word-wrap: break-word;
                 "
          >
        {{AccountNumber}}
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 color: #383d49;
                 white-space: nowrap;
                 "
          >
        貨幣：
      </th>
      <td
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 word-wrap: break-word;
                 "
          >
        {{Currency}}
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 color: #383d49;
                 white-space: nowrap;
                 "
          >
        金額：
      </th>
      <td
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 word-wrap: break-word;
                 "
          >
        $ {{Amount}}
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
  <p>
    若要查看您的提款記錄，請登錄到您賬戶的
    <a
       target="_blank"
       href="https://cfds-portal.thebcr.com/"
       style="
              color: #383d49;
              text-decoration: none;
              font-weight: 700;
              "
       >我的BCR</a
      >
    部分。
  </p>
</div>
', '');
INSERT INTO cms."_TopicContent" ("Id", "TopicId", "CreatedOn", "UpdatedOn", "Language", "Title", "Author", "Content", "Subtitle") VALUES (10052, 11252, '2023-08-16 01:14:21.362505 +00:00', '2023-09-14 20:02:25.143765 +00:00', 'zh-tw', '提现失败', '', e'<div style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px">
  <p style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 24px">
    尊敬的客戶，
  </p>
  <p>
    您的提款請求無法處理並已被拒絕。以下提供更多詳細信息：
  </p>
  <table
         class="letter-table"
         style="
                table-layout: fixed;
                line-height: 24px;
                margin-left: auto;
                margin-right: auto;
                text-align: left;
                padding: 8px;
                float: none;
                "
         bgcolor="#f2f2f2"
         align="left"
         >
    <tr>
      <th
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 color: #383d49;
                 white-space: nowrap;
                 "
          >
        帳戶號碼：
      </th>
      <td
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 word-wrap: break-word;
                 "
          >
        {{AccountNumber}}
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 color: #383d49;
                 white-space: nowrap;
                 "
          >
        帳戶名稱：
      </th>
      <td
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 word-wrap: break-word;
                 "
          >
        {{NativeName}}
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 color: #383d49;
                 white-space: nowrap;
                 "
          >
        帳戶貨幣：
      </th>
      <td
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 word-wrap: break-word;
                 "
          >
        {{Currency}}
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 color: #383d49;
                 white-space: nowrap;
                 "
          >
        提款金額：
      </th>
      <td
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 word-wrap: break-word;
                 "
          >
        $ {{FormattedAmount}}
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <th
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 color: #383d49;
                 white-space: nowrap;
                 "
          >
        請求日期：
      </th>
      <td
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 word-wrap: break-word;
                 "
          >
        {{Date}}
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
  <p>
    提款無法處理的原因是：
  </p>
  <p style="color: #cc1f1a; font-weight: 600">{{Reason}}</p>
  <br />
  <p>
    如果您仍然不確定您的提款請求被拒絕的原因，請諮詢您的帳戶經理或通過在線聊天與我們聯繫。
  </p>
</div>
', '');
INSERT INTO cms."_TopicContent" ("Id", "TopicId", "CreatedOn", "UpdatedOn", "Language", "Title", "Author", "Content", "Subtitle") VALUES (11421, 11276, '2023-09-16 00:44:08.523059 +00:00', '2024-04-04 22:20:51.195449 +00:00', 'vi-vn', 'Khách hàng đã hủy rút tiền', '', e'<div style="font-size: 12px; line-height: 20px">
