  </p>
  <table
         class="letter-table"
         style="
                table-layout: fixed;
                line-height: 24px;
                margin-left: auto;
                margin-right: auto;
                text-align: left;
                padding: 8px;
                float: none;
                "
         bgcolor="#f2f2f2"
         align="left"
         >
    <tr>
      <th
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 color: #383d49;
                 white-space: nowrap;
                 "
          >
        Số tài khoản:
      </th>
      <td
          style="
                 padding-left: 24px;
                 padding-right: 24px;
                 word-wrap: break-word;
